OL,3,CMP responds after concerns district
OL,4,Ccouncil could switch counties
OL,6,FErewash's MP has moved to play down
OL,7,Frumours the district could become part
OL,8,Fof Nottinghamshire under government
OL,9,Fplans to restructure local authorities.
OL,11,FThe district of Erewash sits between
OL,12,FDerby and Nottingham, and is currently
OL,13,Fpart of Derbyshire.
OL,15,FIt is a two-tier local authority area,
OL,16,Fas it has its own borough council, and
OL,17,Ffalls under Derbyshire County Council.
OL,19,FThe government has said it will remove
OL,20,Fall two-tier areas, so that each area
OL,21,Fis governed by one council only.
