OL,3,CMP responds after concerns district
OL,4,Ccouncil could switch counties
OL,6,FAfter rumours emerged that Erewash
OL,7,Fcould become part of Nottinghamshire
OL,8,Funder these plans, Erewash MP Adam
OL,9,FThompson released a video on social
OL,10,Fmedia.
OL,12,FHe said: "Erewash is always going to
OL,13,Fbe part of the historical county of
OL,14,FDerbyshire.
OL,16,F"Councils like Erewash, are going to
OL,17,Fcease to exist - the point is to
OL,18,Fconsolidate local government to
OL,19,Fdeliver better services more
OL,20,Fefficiently.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
