OL,3,CMP responds after concerns district
OL,4,Ccouncil could switch counties
OL,6,FJames Dawson, Leader of Erewash
OL,7,FBorough Council, said: "Nothing has
OL,8,Fbeen decided. The difficulty for us is
OL,9,Fwe are in the middle of two cities.
OL,11,F"It's an administrative boundary,
OL,12,Frather than historic county
OL,13,Fboundaries, but we are still waiting
OL,14,Ffor clarification from the government
OL,15,Faround those boundaries."
